-- Sinopec Group Completes Acquisition of Four Oil, Gas Blocks From Hupecol
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-12-31T04:03:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-31/sinopec-group-completes-acquisition-of-four-oil-gas-blocks-from-hupecol.html
China Petrochemical Corp. has
completed the purchase of four oil and gas blocks from Hupecol
LLC, Sinopec International Petroleum Exploration and Production
Corp., a unit of the Chinese company, said in a statement on its
website today. The unit signed an agreement to buy the assets in
August, Sinopec International said, without giving further
details.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Winnie Zhu in Shanghai at 
